partners pay us per subscription while hedge fund managers pay half the price and also sign up for a free version of the products the company offers on september   one of slim’s companies announced that philosophy jr studio a fashion line for young women will expand into a standalone retailer chain that will compete with elite fashion retailers across the globe although the style of the new fashion line and the number of yearly collections has not been made public philosophy jr studio is expected to compete with a myriad of wellknown multinational fastfashion retailers such as hm forever  zara and ca the fashion line will be offered at individual brick and mortar boutiques at two shopping malls in mexico city with a us million seed investment slims plan is to have  standalone stores by  the brand was established in  and has been sold at sears mexico a unit of grupo sanborns the restaurant retail and pharmacy chain owned by slim family and personal lifeedit slim’s father khalil salim haddad aglamaz emigrated to mexico from lebanon then part of the ottoman empire in  he was  and later changed his name to julián slim haddad it was not uncommon for lebanese children to be sent abroad before they reached the age of  to avoid being conscripted into the ottoman army and four of haddads older brothers were already living in mexico at the time of his arrival in  julián established a dry goods store la estrella de oriente the star of the orient la estrella de oriente was an important dry goods store located on venustiano carranza where it had merchandise worth more than  by january   only ten years after the business was founded by  he had begun investing in real estate in the flourishing commercial district of mexico city where julián would acquire prime real estate at fire sale prices and in zocalo district during the – mexican revolution by  juliáns net worth reached  pesos and was diversified within various assets including real estate businesses and various stocks in aug