but prefers to write by hand instead of on a computer due to the vast size of his business empire slim often jokes that he cant keep track of all the companies he manages carlos slim is a maronite catholic and he is one of the prominent backers of legion of christ a roman catholic religious institute personal fortuneedit wealthedit on march   slim surpassed american investor warren buffett as the worlds second richest person with an estimated net worth of us billion compared with buffets us billion on august   the wall street journal ran a cover story profiling slim the article said while the market value of his stake in publicly traded companies could decline at any time at the moment he is probably wealthier than bill gates according to the wall street journal slim credits part of his ability to discover investment opportunities early to the writings of his friend futurist author alvin toffler on august   fortune magazine reported that slim had overtaken gates as the worlds richest person slims estimated fortune soared to us billion based on the value of his public holdings at the end of july gates net worth was estimated to be at least us billion on march   forbes ranked slim as the worlds secondrichest person behind warren buffett and ahead of bill gates on march   forbes ranked slim as the worlds thirdrichest person behind gates and buffett and ahead of larry ellison on march   forbes once again reported that slim had overtaken gates as the worlds richest person with a net worth of us billion at the time gates and buffett had a net worth of us billion and us billion respectively he was the first mexican to top the list it was the first time in  years that the person on top of the list was not from the united states it was also the first time the person at the top of the list was from an emerging economy between  and  slim more than doubled his net worth from  to  billion in march  forbes stated that slim had maintained his position as the wealthiest person in the world with his fortune estimated at us billion in december  according to the bloomberg billionaires index carlos slim helú remained the worlds richest person with an estimated net worth of us billion on march   forbes stated that slim was still maintaining his firstplace position as the wealthiest person in the world with an estimated net worth of us billion on may   bloomberg lp ranked slim the secondrichest person in the world after bill gates on july   forbes announced that slim had reclaimed the position of the wealthiest person in the world with a fortune of us billion in september  forbes listed slim as number  on its list of billionaires with a net worth of us billion as of december  his net worth is us billion real estateedit slim lives in a bedroom home in the lomas de chapultepec district of mexico city close to where he grew up that has been his residence for over  years slims real estate holding company inmobiliaria carso develops invests owns and operates many residential and commercial properties across mexico the company owns over  shopping centers including ten in mexico city and operates stores in the country under us brands including the mexican arms of saks fifth avenue sears and the coffee factory slim has been making private real estate investments around the world particularly in the united states he has been reported to have acquired  fifth avenue an story office tower for us million and also a piece of the former new york times building on west rd street he controls approximately  acres of prime beverly hills real estate at the corner of wilshire and santa monica boulevards in may  slim opened inbursa aquarium latin americas largest aquarium slim owns the duke seamans mansion a  beaux arts house on th avenue in new york city which he bought for  million in  the mansion is  square feet and has  bedrooms  bathrooms and a doctors office in the basement in may  he listed the property for sale at  million nearly twice what he had paid in april  slim bought the marquette building in detroit and purchased pepsico americas beverages headquarters in somers new york for us million slim owns a second mansion in new york city at  w th st which he leased early in  to the john barrett salon for us million annually the property was bought in  for us million philanthropyedit slim has been publicly skeptical of the giving pledge by bill gates and warren buffett giving away at least half of their fortunes but—according to his spokesman—he devoted us billion or roughly  to his carlos slim foundation as of  though slim has not gone as far as gates and buffett in pledging more than half of his fortune slim has expressed firm support for philanthropy and has advised budding entrepreneurs that businessmen must do more than give‍—‌they should participate in solving problems slim has channeled his philanthropic endeavors into many initiatives such as funding a genomic medicine research project subsidizing numerous arts and education projects in mexico city including the museo soumaya named after his late wife which displays his art collection for no admission fee slim founded three nonprofit foundations concentrating on mexico city one for the arts education and health care one for sports and one for downtown restoration fundación carlos slim helúedit established in  fundación carlos slim helú sponsors the museo soumaya in mexico city named after slims late wife soumaya domit opened  it holds  pieces including religious relics contains the worlds secondlargest collection of rodin sculptures including the kiss the largest dalí collection in latin america works by leonardo da vinci pablo picasso pierreauguste renoir and coins from the viceroys of spain the inauguration in  was attended by the president of mexico nobel prize laureates writers and other celebrities after stating that he had donated us billion of dividends to fundación carlos slim helú us billion in  and another us billion in  slim was ranked fifth in forbes worlds biggest givers in may  education and health care projects have included  million to perform  cataract surgeries in peru through the clinton initiative a us million fund to strengthen small and mediumsize businesses in colombia and a digital education program for youth in mexico us million for programs in nutrition and disease prevention in central america with the bill  melinda gates foundation and the government of spain us million to work with the world wildlife fund on restoration of six areas for species in mexico including the monarch butterfly and us million on education programs for young people through colombian singer shakiras alas foundation fundación telmexedit in  slim established fundación telmex a broadranging philanthropic foundation which as he announced in  had been provided with an asset base of us billion to establish carso institutes for health sports and education furthermore it was to work in support of an initiative of bill clinton to aid the people of latin america because mexican foundations are not required to publish their financial information it is not possible to confirm slims claims of charitable giving through a public source the foundation has organized copa telmex an amateur sports tournament recognized in  and  by guinness world records as having the most participants of any such tournament in the world together with fundación carlos slim helú telmex announced in  that it was to invest more than us million in mexican sports programs from grassroots level to olympic standard telmex sponsored the sauber f team for the  season   telmex donated at least  million to the clinton foundation fundación del centro histórico de la ciudad de méxico acedit in  slim and exbroadcaster jacobo zabludowsky organized the fundación del centro histórico de la ciudad de méxico ac mexico city historic center foundation to revitalize and rescue mexico citys historic downtown area to enable more people to live work and find entertainment there he has been chair of the council for the restoration of the historic downtown of mexico city since  in  he along with the president of mexico mexico city mayor and mexico city archbishop inaugurated the first phase of plaza mariana close to basilica de guadalupe the complex whose construction was funded by slim includes an evangelization center museum columbarium health center and market awardsedit entrepreneurial merit medal of honor in  from mexicos chamber of commerce gold patron of the american academy of achievement commander in the belgian order of leopold ii ceo of the year in  by latin trade magazine ceo of the decade in  by latin trade magazine fundacion telmex received in  the national sports prize of mexico for sports promotion in  his philanthropy was recognised with the award of the national order of the cedar by the lebanese government in  the hispanic society of america awarded fundacion carlos slim the sorolla medal for its contribution to the arts and culture on may   slim was awarded a honorary doctorate in public service from george washington university criticismedit slims growing fortune has been a subject of controversy because it has been amassed in a developing country where average per capita income does not surpass us a year and nearly  of the population lives in poverty critics claim that slim is a monopolist pointing to telmexs control of  of the mexican landline telephone market slims wealth is the equivalent of roughly  of mexicos annual economic output telmex of which  is owned by slim and his family charges among the highest usage fees in the world according to the organisation for economic cooperation and development the average mexican spends  pesos per day on slims goods and services for a total of roughly us million a day and the federal telecommunications institute a new mexican government antimonopoly watchdog said in april  that slims telecom businesses are monopolies slims business presence in mexico alone is so broad that many mexicans find it appropriate to call the country slimlandia as it is almost impossible to go a day in mexico without contributing to slims wealth according to celso garrido economist at the universidad nacional autónoma de méxico slims domination of mexicos conglomerates prevents the growth of smaller companies resulting in a shortage of paying jobs forcing many mexicans to seek better lives in the us in response to the criticism slim has stated when you live for others opinions you are dead i dont want to live thinking about how ill be remembered by mexican people claiming indifference about his position on forbes list of the worlds richest people he has said he has no interest in becoming the worlds richest person when asked to explain his sudden increase in wealth at a press conference soon after forbes annual rankings were published he said the stock market goes up  and down and noted that his fortune could quickly drop slim was criticized by the dutch minister of economic affairs henk kamp in  for attempting to expand his telecom empire beyond the americas by américa móvils buyout offer to kpn a dutch landline and mobile telecommunications company privatized in the s by stating an acquisition of kpn by a foreign company could have consequences for the netherlands national security two years after slims failed bid to take over the company mainly due to political intervention and slims paucity of interest in purchasing the company slims america movil sab began offering  billion euros of bonds that can be converted into shares of royal kpn nv america movil now controls a  percent stake of kpn with a market value of  billion euros as of may   slim has been slowly decreasing his holdings since he was forced to withdraw a  billion euro bid for the dutch phone line carrier in  after negotiations broke down and kpns preference share foundation blocked the takeover attempt referencesedit  a b c d e where does carlos slim keep his money adam hayes retrieved april     a b c carl