computer and instead prefers to keep all his financial data in thoroughly kept notebooks slim is well versed in technology but prefers to write by hand instead of on a computer due to the vast size of his business empire slim often jokes that he cant keep track of all the companies he manages carlos slim is a maronite catholic and he is one of the prominent backers of legion of christ a roman catholic religious institute personal fortuneedit wealthedit on march   slim surpassed american investor warren buffett as the worlds second richest person with an estimated net worth of us billion compared with buffets us billion on august   the wall street journal ran a cover story profiling slim the article said while the market value of his stake in publicly traded companies could decline at any time at the moment he is probably wealthier than bill gates according to the wall street journal slim credits part of his ability to discover investment opportunities early to the writings of his friend futurist author alvin toffler on august   fortune magazine reported that slim had overtaken gates as the worlds richest person slims estimated fortune soared to us billion based on the value of his public holdings at the end of july gates net worth was estimated to be at least us billion on march   forbes ranked slim as the worlds secondrichest person behind warren buffett and ahead of bill gates on march   forbes ranked slim as the worlds thirdrichest person behind gates and buffett and ahead of larry ellison on march   forbes once again reported that slim had overtaken gates as the worlds richest person with a net worth of us billion at the time gates and buffett had a net worth of us billion and us billion respectively he was the first mexican to top the list it was the first time in  years that the person on top of the list was not from the united states it was also the first time the person at the top of the list was from an emerging economy between  and  slim more than doubled his net worth from  to  billion in march  forbes stated that slim had maintained his position as the wealthiest person in the world with his fortune estimated at us billion in december  according to the bloomberg billionaires index carlos slim helú remained the worlds richest person with an estimated net worth of us billion on march   forbes stated that slim was still maintaining his firstplace position as the wealthiest person in the world with an estimated net worth of us billion on may   bloomberg lp ranked slim the secondrichest person in the world after bill gates on july   forbes announced that slim had reclaimed the position of the wealthiest person in the world with a fortune of us billion in september  forbes listed slim as number  on its list of billionaires with a net worth of us billion as of december  his net worth is us billion real estateedit slim lives in a bedroom home in the lomas de chapultepec district of mexico city close to where he grew up that has been his residence for over  years slims real estate holding company inmobiliaria carso develops invests owns and operates many residential and commercial properties across mexico the company owns over  shopping centers including ten in mexico city and operates stores in the country under us brands including the mexican arms of saks fifth avenue sears and the coffee factory slim has been making private real estate investments around the world particularly in the united states he has been reported to have acquired  fifth avenue an story office tower for us million and also a piece of the former new york times building on west rd street he controls approximately  acres of prime beverly hills real estate at the corner of wilshire and santa monica boulevards in may  slim opened inbursa aquarium latin americas largest aquarium slim owns the duke seamans mansion a  beaux arts house on th avenue in new york city which he bought for  million in  the mansion is  square feet and has  bedrooms  bathrooms and a