 we are aware of how our work impacts the daily lives of many individuals and companies and of course mexico in addition to the direct jobs it generates through its financing activities savings and insurance inbursa is a factor in the quality of life for more than  million  thousand customers through the acquisition investment funds and pensions inbursa contributes to the growth of the assets of its customers giving them confidence tranquility and a better future in the insurance business inbursa customers have all the support and resources they need in the worst moments death disease theft accident fire protecting their loved ones and their property which have gotten so hard  providing funding to individuals inbursa allows many families to have a house or other assets thereby supporting the formation of their heritage with credits that give companies they accelerate their growth by investing more in the country and generating more and better jobs it is noteworthy that at times has been more critical global funding restriction while the banking sector has had a fall inbursa besides being in the process of opening more than  branches over the past year and a half has doubled the extension of credit reaching  billion pesos this includes smes where we have a growth rate of over  new loans each month in the strategic partnership that we started in  with la caixa in barcelona looked at the activity and financial vision of both institutions but above all the values and principles that we identify both groups we have a mutual interest in contributing to the welfare of society and both groups have very relevant activities to help those most in need la caixa de barcelona through its social work chaired by don isidro fainé who is an example for his outstanding leadership and business work but it is more for his intense effective and committed work for others in our case mainly through the foundation carlos slim and telmex both created chaired and led by mr carlos slim who with great sensitivity and dedication applies his extraordinary ability to understand problems and find the best solutions to contribute to the attention of major setbacks in our society it is through this shared belief and commitment we are announcing today the creation of inbursa foundation focused on what matters most is the impact for present and future welfare of the population most in need namely health education justice employment and culture inbursa foundation is one more link in activities that benefit society more than  years we have developed with the fundación carlos slim i would emphasize that we are very honored to have this event with the presence of his highness the infanta doña cristina who works with fundación la caixa leading prominently the international cooperation area whose work has benefited many countries in inbursa we clear our responsibility with mexico with society and with our customers and so from now inbursa foundation begins operations with a strong commitment to continue contributing to more and more people live longer and better thank you very much     could you forward this site to marco antonio slim domit   microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings privacy or help documentation sign in hold on… we’re sorry but this didn’t work you can’t turn off personalized ads right now because your browser is currently blocking thirdparty cookies we can help you fix this issue let’s get started depending on what browser you use open options or settings make sure that thirdparty cookies are not blocked anymore to find out how search your browser’s help revisit httpchoicemicrosoftcomoptout and then on the “personalized ads in this browser” tile 